{
  "id": "69a806db567b3f41674d4a88",
  "title": "評価懸念",
  "created": 1772619487,
  "updated": 1772619520,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a806db567b3f41674d4a88",
      "text": "評価懸念",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619487,
      "updated": 1772619487
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806df000000000037728b",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619487,
      "updated": 1772619493
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806e0000000000037728c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619488,
      "updated": 1772619488
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806fe000000000037728d",
      "text": "放課後、空き教室。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619519,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037728e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037728f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377290",
      "text": "ねえねえ、今日のテーマいきまーす。「評価懸念」！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377291",
      "text": "つまりさ、「どう思われてるか気になってムリ」ってやつ。通知来るだけで心臓バクバクするあの現象ね。わかる人、挙手〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377292",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377293",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]（やさしく）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377294",
      "text": "はい、挙手します。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377295",
      "text": "ふーこちゃん、それ、とても自然なことですよ。誰だって人からどう見られているかは気になりますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377296",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377297",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]（淡々と）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377298",
      "text": "正式には「他者からの評価を過度に気にする傾向」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377299",
      "text": "特に思春期は自己意識が強まる時期だから、統計的にも増える。珍しくない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729c",
      "text": "出た、ひよりのデータ砲。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729d",
      "text": "でもさ〜、わかっててもムリなときあるじゃん？インスタに写真あげて、いいね少なかったら「え、わたし空気？」ってなるやつ。あれ、なんなん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037729f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a0",
      "text": "それはね、自分の価値を「数字」に結びつけてしまうからかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a1",
      "text": "本当は写真一枚で人の価値なんて決まりませんのに。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a3",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a4",
      "text": "承認欲求の外部依存。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a5",
      "text": "自分の「これでいい」という基準より、他人の反応を優先してしまう状態。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a6",
      "text": "アルゴリズム、つまり表示の仕組みにも左右されるから、必ずしも実力や魅力と比例しない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772a9",
      "text": "アルゴ…なんだっけ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ab",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ac",
      "text": "簡単に言うと「見せる順番を決めてるシステム」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ad",
      "text": "だから、いいねが少ない＝ダメ、ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772af",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b0",
      "text": "あ〜、つまり「たまたま表示されにくかっただけ説」もあるってこと？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b1",
      "text": "それ聞いたらちょい救われるわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b3",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b4",
      "text": "でもね、ふーこちゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b5",
      "text": "救われたと感じた自分の気持ちも大切にしてくださいね。数字よりも、「私はこれが好き」と思えたことの方が、ずっと大事ですから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b8",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんみ…沁みる…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ba",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772bc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772bd",
      "text": "でもさ、評価懸念ってSNSだけじゃなくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772be",
      "text": "授業で発表するときとか、「変なこと言ったらどうしよ」って思って黙っちゃう人もいるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c0",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c1",
      "text": "それは「失敗回避の思考」が強く働いている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c2",
      "text": "人は得をするより、損を避けるほうを優先しやすい。心理実験でも確認されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c5",
      "text": "あー、わかる。「スベるくらいなら喋らん」ってやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c7",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c8",
      "text": "でも、ひよりちゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772c9",
      "text": "失敗を怖がる気持ちは悪いものではありませんよね？自分を守ろうとしている証拠でもありますから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772cb",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772cc",
      "text": "否定はしない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772cd",
      "text": "ただ、守りすぎると成長機会を失う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ce",
      "text": "リスクをゼロにするより、「小さく失敗する練習」を積むほうが合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d1",
      "text": "小さく失敗、ねえ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d2",
      "text": "テストでいきなり100点目指すより、まず60点でも出す、みたいな？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d4",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d5",
      "text": "近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d6",
      "text": "発表なら、完璧を狙わず「一言だけ発言する」など、ハードルを下げる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d8",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772d9",
      "text": "それなら、怖さも少し和らぎそうですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772da",
      "text": "「全部うまくやらなくていい」と思えるだけで、心は軽くなります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772dc",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772de",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772df",
      "text": "でもさー、結局「どう思われるか」ってゼロにはならんくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e0",
      "text": "人間、他人の目からは逃げられんじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e2",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e3",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e4",
      "text": "評価懸念を消すのではなく、「扱えるようにする」のが現実的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e6",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e7",
      "text": "扱う、ですか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772e9",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ea",
      "text": "評価には二種類ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772eb",
      "text": " 1. 自分を成長させるフィードバック",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ec",
      "text": " 2. ただの好みや感想",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ed",
      "text": "この区別をするだけで、精神的ダメージは減る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ef",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f0",
      "text": "あー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f1",
      "text": "「それ、改善できる系？」か「ただのディス？」か分けるってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f2",
      "text": "確かに全部真に受けてたらメンタル死ぬ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f4",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f5",
      "text": "でも、傷ついた気持ちを無理に切り分けなくてもいいんですよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f6",
      "text": "まずは「傷ついた」と認めてあげてください。そこから、ひよりちゃんの言うように整理していけばいいのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f8",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772f9",
      "text": "感情の受容は、思考の前提条件。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772fa",
      "text": "ましろの言うことは合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772fc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772fd",
      "text": "え、今のってほぼ「ましろ正しい」宣言では？レアすぎ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff00000000003772ff",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377300",
      "text": "事実を述べただけ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377301",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377302",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377303",
      "text": "ふふ。ありがとうございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377304",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377305",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377306",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377307",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめモード）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377308",
      "text": "というわけで本日の鼎談まとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377309",
      "text": " 評価が気になるのは仕様。バグじゃない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730a",
      "text": " 数字や反応＝自分の価値、ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730b",
      "text": " 小さく挑戦して、小さく失敗しよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730c",
      "text": " 意見は「役立つやつ」と「ただの感想」に仕分け。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730d",
      "text": " 傷ついたら、まず自分をよしよし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037730f",
      "text": "どうよ、これ。わりと神回じゃない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377310",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377311",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377312",
      "text": "妥当。再現性もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377313",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377314",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377315",
      "text": "ええ、とても素敵なお話でした。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377316",
      "text": "評価に振り回されすぎず、それでも人とつながることを大切にできたらいいですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377317",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377318",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377319",
      "text": "よーし、じゃあ今日は解散！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731a",
      "text": "次回テーマ「黒歴史との向き合い方」でどう？需要しかなくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731c",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731d",
      "text": "統計的に高い需要が見込まれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff000000000037731f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377320",
      "text": "またゆっくり、お話ししましょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377321",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    },
    {
      "id": "69a806ff0000000000377322",
      "text": "（放課後のチャイムが鳴る。）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772619520,
      "updated": 1772619520
    }
  ]
}